name: L-arginine,2-oxoglutarate:oxygen oxidoreductase (succinate-forming); L-arginine,2-oxoglutarate:oxygen 5-oxidoreductase (1-pyrroline-5-carboxylate-forming)
definition: 2-Oxoglutarate + L-Arginine + Oxygen <=> Succinate + CO2 + Guanidine + (S)-1-Pyrroline-5-carboxylate + H2O
comment: 2-oxoglutarate-dependent ethylene/succinate-forming enzyme (catalyzing R09784 and R09785 at the rate of 2:1) two-step reaction (see R10081+R10082)
